.ue 1
                                                                       $.#$
                                                     Calicut 29th June 1859
My sweet Frederic

.ue 2
                                                                       $.#$
Forts.: 29th June 1859
I thank you for the few last lines you wrote me. I was glad to hear dear
Papa found you in better health than we had expected. I hope you injoy your
dear papa very much and that you tell him all your heart all your thoughts
with out any fear or restrain, for he will understand you and with great
love help you and do you good! loose no time while you have him to bring
out of your little heart the dark and sad thoughts which make you some time
unhappy.

Do you pray my sweet Child? Ask papa what is faith and having told you he
will pray for you, with you. With faith you can get every thing from God.
Memory, wisdome a new heart, a joyful mind, love, humility. all good gifts
Adieu my very precious son.
.fo -
                              Your Mama J. G.


